channel.title: Elven Camp
channel.description:
Ok, I've found the elven camp, but nothings there. I'm just wondering if anyone could make a custom area for me, thats nearly large enough for the area. I'm sort of trying to make it a battle/city type theme. These are the coords: [code]2264,3341[/code]
If you do spawn the objects will it lag, and if so is there a way to make it not lag?
Thanks.

item.title: Elven Camp
item.dc:creator: @clest clest
item.description:
@clest wrote:

It depends on many things if it will lag

1.You have to try and see if it laggs first (common sense)

2.How your computer runs e.g speed type

3.The source you are using (as some sources are lagg free!)

4.How many of the object you want to enter

Hope this helped a little
